
1  Kane jo-Asuria mane pod nie hembegi owinjo gima osetimore, ne gibwok ahinya, 
2  kendo luoro gi kihondko nomakogi ma ji ariyo na ok nyal yud kanyachiel. Giduto ne gike ka giringo ka ging’ado e pap gi gode. 
3  Jolwenjgi mane osebedo kojot e gode molworo Bethulia bende noringo. Eka jolwenj jo-Israel duto nowuok momwomore kuomgi. 
4  Uzia bende nooro joote Betomasthaim, gi Bebai, gi Choba, gi Kola, kod piny gode duto mag Israel, mondo onyis joma odak kuondego gima osetimore, kendo ojiwgi giduto gimwuomre kuom wasikgi mondo gitiekgi. 
5  Gikanyono mane jo-Israel owinjoe wachno, ne gio kuom wasikgi duto kanyakla, kendo ne ginegogi nyaka Choba. Jo-Jerusalem kaachiel gi joma odak e piny gode duto bende kane owinjo gima osetimore e kambi wasigu, ne jobiro mondo okony jowetegi. Eka jo-Gilead gi jo-Galili bende nomonjo jo-Asuria gi yoka bathgi monegogi achadha nyaka ne gikadho Damaski gi piny mokiewo kode, 
6  Jo-Bethulia mane oyudo odong’ dala, to noo e kambi jo-Asuria moyako mwandu mogundho, 
7  kendo jo-Israel mane odwogo koa nego wasigu nokawo gik moko mane giyudo kodong’. To joma nodak e mier madongo gi matindo mane nie gode gi pap, bende noyako gik mathoth, nikech gik moko ne ng’eny ahinya.

Jo-Israel ogoyo erokamano


8  Joakim jadolo maduong’ kod jodong buch Israel mane odak Jerusalem, nobiro mondo one gik madongo mane Ruoth Nyasaye osetimo ni joge, kendo mondo gine Judith, kendo gigone erokamano. 
9  Kane gichopo e ode, ne gipake gi dwol achiel ka giwacho niya,

“In e duong’ mar Jerusalem,

kendo in e sunga mar jo-Israel.

Adier, in e osimbo mar ogandawa!


10  Jo-Israel nyaka goni erokamano maduong’

kuom gik moko duto

ma isetimo gi lueti iwuon

Nyaka Nyasaye bende yie chutho

gi gima isetimo.

Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto

mondo oguedhi nyaka chieng’!”

Eka ji duto nodwoko ni. “Amin!”


11  Jo-Israel noyako kambi jo-Asuria kuom ndalo piero adek, kendo ne gimiyo Judith hemb Holoferno kaachiel gi gige mag mesa mag fedha duto, gi kombene gi bakundene mag metho, kod gik moko duto mane nie hembe. Moko kuom gigo Judith noting’o gi kanyna, to moko modong’ nodhuro e geche ma dhok ywayo mi odhigo. 
12  Mond jo-Israel duto noreto kabiro mondo onene, kendo ne gichuogone wer ka gimielne mondo gimiyego duong’. Judith to nokawo oboke mag yien momiyo mon mane ni kode. En owuon gi jowetene to ne gisidho osimbo mag oboke mag yiend zeituni. 
13  Eka nodhi motelo ni mon mane miel kendo ne gimiel giduto. Jo-Israel machwo duto noluwo bang’gi ka miel, koting’o gilwenjegi kendo kogawore gi maua modol ka tach. 
14  Judith nochako wero wer magoyogo ni Nyasaye erokamano, ka jo-Isarel duto olwore, kendo ne giwer giduto niya,

